{"tid":206642,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日三餐 18/04/2017","createTime":"2017-04-18T13:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T09:14:55.000Z","uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a2280facd351ce612f8bcb42286ae17b560b1a","tid":206642,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"胃潰瘍好得7788 終於有番啲胃口食野<br />\n本身已經瘦底 依家病完得番100磅鬆啲<br />\n想試下係度記錄低自己每日食過既野<br />\n順便提醒自己每日要食多啲<br />\n<br />\n#早餐<br />\n琴日焗定既包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7UdVS89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7UdVS89.jpg&h=69178909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#午餐<br />\n生菜豬潤瘦肉湯飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/210249_aa7184b1ed8496badfa40117a3794892.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F210249_aa7184b1ed8496badfa40117a3794892.jpg&h=c75cecfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#晚餐 <br />\n出街食左幾日 都係屋企飯好食啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/17b5147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F17b5147.jpg&h=ffddcd18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6749d24b332814ef585a61b5413a6cbdba38e705","tid":206642,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:16:18.000Z","msg":"狗糧咩"},{"pid":"28977425d507667d033f17d48a2e7758bf8632c5","tid":206642,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"晚餐好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14890eafb5b830f7ad109a48177fe781c6661159","tid":206642,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗糧咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets